snippet.title: Super Mario Construct - F3 2020 Full Trailer (Revised)
snippet.description:
Super Mario Construct is a HTML5 game, graphically styled after SMW and it's a fan game with a IeveI editor, infinite customization and various tiles/objects/enemies/power-ups/etc. of different 2D/3D Mario games!

You can play Super Mario Construct by clicking this link: https://luigibonus.com/games/supermarioconstruct/

Consider also joining our Discord servers below!

Level Share Square: https://discord.gg/nEryqJC7aq
Super Mario Construct: https://discord.gg/zbjpJ3jB

Trailer Music by Qumu: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W9urNCVWhn8

Game developed by Luigibonus
Trailer and small revisions by Mariomaster7771 (BluSeven)

#SuperMarioConstruct #F3
